import React, { useState } from 'react';
import './MuscleMap.css';

const MuscleMapFull = () => (
  <svg
    id="Layer_2"
    data-name="Layer 2"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    viewBox="0 0 768.41 607.66"
  >
    <defs>
      <style>{`
        .body { fill: rgba(175, 175, 175, 0.1); }
        .calves, .hamstrings, .glutes, .adductors-back, .abductors-back,
        .lower-back, .lats, .traps, .neck, .rear-delts, .triceps,
        .forearms-underside, .quads, .adductors-abductors-front, .abs,
        .obliques, .pecs, .front-side-delts, .biceps, .forearms-top {
          fill: #a12c2c;
        }
      `}</style>
    </defs>

    <g id="Body_Fill" data-name="Body Fill">
      <path
        id="Posterior"
        className="body"
        d="M651.82,462.98c-4.39-55.93... (truncated)"
      />
      <path
        id="Anterior"
        className="body"
        d="M263.15,467.02c-.21-.55... (truncated)"
      />
    </g>

    <g id="Posterior_View_Muscles" data-name="Posterior View Muscles">
      <g id="Calves">
        <path
          className="calves"
          d="M522.19,464.16c-10.64.77... (truncated)"
        />
        <path
          className="calves"
          d="M639.16,460.15c-29.57... (truncated)"
        />
      </g>
      {/* ... other groups like Hamstrings, Glutes, Adductors, etc. */}
    </g>

    <g id="Anterior_View_Muscles" data-name="Anterior View Muscles">
      <g id="Quads">
        <path
          className="quads"
          d="M151.01,315.88c-6.67... (truncated)"
        />
        <path
          className="quads"
          d="M228.64,315.88c6.67... (truncated)"
        />
      </g>
      {/* ... continue for other muscle groups */}
    </g>
  </svg>
);


export default MuscleMapFull;
